      "content": "but that sounds so exhausting. like the only way to actually find peace is to keep fighting this war that I'm already losing. doesn't it ever just feel... logical? like if the pain is constant, why is it \"wrong\" to want the pain to stop? doesn't everyone deserve a way out when it gets too much?",
